org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.ebxml

Interface EbXMLClassification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EbXMLSlotList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EbXMLClassification21, EbXMLClassification30

    public interface EbXMLClassification
extends EbXMLSlotList
    Encapsulation of the ebXML classes for ClassificationType.

    This class contains convenience methods and provides a version independent abstraction of the ebXML data structure.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider
